      },
      "date": "2017-06-13 09:28:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nDear Faccini,\n\nI found this problem when I rebased your RAoLU patch to 2.7 and ran tests. It was easy to found this problem since half of the sanity_hsm tests failed.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
